g.text: Proportions of moves out of each node, 28 Oct 2017 to 30 Apr 2025. Only moves above a threshold are included (0.070, 7.0% or more of moves from that node, minimum of 3 moves between nodes, or 3, whichever is larger). 'n' = total number of people; 'n₀' = number resident on the first date. 3755 individuals.
